WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.120 --> 00:00:20.025
Hey, good morning family, praise the Lord, or good afternoon, wherever you are.

00:00:20.025 --> 00:00:30.800
Hello, welcome, thank you for joining us.

00:00:31.600 --> 00:00:33.813
It's 2025.

00:00:33.813 --> 00:00:49.260
We're right now at New Year's Eve doing this video.

00:00:49.260 --> 00:01:11.180
I've been interceding for this New Year all the last several days.

00:01:11.180 --> 00:01:51.555
We've had such intense intercession going on in our house, praying for the nations and asking what the Lord has in store for 2025.

00:01:51.555 --> 00:01:58.270
This is a very serious time.

00:02:15.720 --> 00:02:41.600
The Lord told me there would be two different words: one for the ones that are awake and one for the ones that are lukewarm.

00:02:41.600 --> 00:03:19.599
You will see the ones that are awake and on fire for Him, who have their lamps full of oil.

00:03:19.599 --> 00:03:43.980
We talked about this remnant of people who will see great change as the harvesters.

00:03:43.980 --> 00:04:17.742
You will see a mighty anointing and a transfer of wealth from the sinner laid up for the righteous.

00:04:17.742 --> 00:04:40.060
If you are staying vertical with Him, you will hear in this window.

00:04:52.544 --> 00:05:25.379
The Lord said, 'I'm giving you a window, remnant; I'm giving you a window for a great acceleration of prosperity and preparation, like the Josephs, for what is coming.

00:05:25.379 --> 00:06:15.253
' How big the window is, I don't know, but he said in this window, if you're listening to Him and staying vertical, you will hear Him on what you're supposed to be doing.

00:06:18.653 --> 00:06:36.029
To the ones that are lukewarm, this will be a time of great shaking to awaken you.

00:06:36.029 --> 00:06:52.480
He said, 'Brandon, I will take care of My beloved.

00:06:52.480 --> 00:07:08.599
' He talked to us about it in an hour-long word.

00:07:08.599 --> 00:07:21.939
He said, 'You are My beloved and I bring gifts.

00:07:21.939 --> 00:07:30.635
' Thank you, Holy Spirit.

00:07:30.635 --> 00:07:59.857
He said, 'I bring gifts to the bride before the Bridegroom comes for the wedding.

00:07:59.857 --> 00:08:49.936
' He said, 'I am standing at the door listening for My Father's instruction for Him to tell Me to come back for My bride.

00:08:49.936 --> 00:09:13.300
' In Jewish tradition, the groom always gives gifts to the bride before the wedding.

00:09:24.413 --> 00:09:34.050
He said He was bringing forth great giftings and romance to the bride.

00:09:45.500 --> 00:10:06.346
He said, 'Brandon, I am the God of the cattle on a thousand hills, for My gifts are great and vast; I have streets of gold.

00:10:06.346 --> 00:10:45.292
' He told me the wealth of the sinner is laid up for the righteous, but it is about a kingly Him; He's the King of kings and the Lord of lords.

00:10:45.292 --> 00:11:36.160
As the Bridegroom is wooing the bride and getting ready for the marriage feast, for the marriage supper of the Lamb, there is a major exchange of romance toward His church.

00:11:36.160 --> 00:11:59.595
I saw an impartation of angelic visitations and manifestations of glory—healings and things your mind cannot comprehend.

00:12:04.244 --> 00:12:19.205
The King is coming, and it is a time of celebration for the bride and the groom.

00:12:24.700 --> 00:12:39.920
He was telling me all this stuff is going to start taking place with a great acceleration of change.

00:12:39.920 --> 00:12:48.392
2025 will be a year of great change.

00:13:01.218 --> 00:13:01.622
Then I heard, 'War, war, war.

00:13:01.622 --> 00:13:19.159
' It will be talked about on the news.

00:13:19.159 --> 00:13:29.820
2025 will be known for war.

00:13:30.244 --> 00:13:46.839
I saw conflict between America and China at the Panama Canal.

00:13:46.839 --> 00:14:43.431
I saw a red dragon flapping its wings, and I heard the Spirit of the Lord say, 'The Panama Canal, for there is great corruption, but as Donald Trump cracks his whip, he will tame the dragon.

00:14:43.431 --> 00:15:17.959
' I saw Donald Trump standing there like a circus ringmaster with a black coat with long tails and a white shirt with a black bow tie.

00:15:19.156 --> 00:15:33.595
He was cracking a whip to tame the dragon.

00:15:35.149 --> 00:16:00.140
I saw the dragon snapping and gnashing its teeth at him, but it was flying backwards as he cracked his whip.

00:16:00.140 --> 00:16:09.720
The dragon was being tamed and retreating.

00:16:13.167 --> 00:16:39.971
A communistic spirit has tried to come over America as an extension from this dragon, but you will see that agenda broken.

00:16:42.759 --> 00:17:07.880
I saw Kim Jong-un and China; they were flapping their wings, and he was taming Kim Jong-un and the Chinese party.

00:17:07.880 --> 00:17:35.964
This is a demonic principality that has tried to influence our government through the Democratic party through hidden doors.

00:17:35.964 --> 00:17:48.840
These things of communism will be broken.

00:17:53.180 --> 00:18:02.811
I saw Justin Trudeau being removed from his position.

00:18:03.086 --> 00:18:43.954
The Lord said there would be a dividing line between the far left and the far right, and you will see a Holy Ghost revival from sea to sea.

00:18:43.954 --> 00:19:00.646
He said even Justin Trudeau and Emmanuel Macron will be dealt with.

00:19:00.646 --> 00:19:22.590
He said because of Macron holding back, he's trying to bring a New World Order over Europe.

00:19:33.184 --> 00:20:02.059
The people of Canada have cried out, and I will deliver thee; there will be revival that breaks forth from shore to shore, and you will soar.

00:20:02.059 --> 00:20:08.760
Justin Trudeau's days are numbered.

00:20:08.760 --> 00:20:38.850
There will be a dividing between the far left and the right, and it will happen overnight.

00:20:47.869 --> 00:21:11.360
He told me He was going to deal with Emmanuel Macron also, but he showed me that there would be great revival in Europe.

00:21:25.813 --> 00:21:41.744
He said, 'You try to stop My gospel, I will deal with you also,' and He spoke of the Antichrist spirit.

00:21:41.744 --> 00:21:53.314
There will be revival in France and Europe.

00:21:53.314 --> 00:22:15.080
Donald Trump will be putting these people in check, dealing with Putin, the bear.

00:22:15.587 --> 00:22:31.306
I saw him cracking his whip across the nations, and it was bringing change.

00:22:41.390 --> 00:22:43.799
A whip only tames the animal; it doesn't destroy it.

00:22:43.799 --> 00:22:50.840
It causes the animal to pause.

00:22:50.840 --> 00:23:20.806
It's about His presence allowing for one last call and bringing freedom for His people to hear.

00:23:20.806 --> 00:23:43.177
It is a window for the last push to bring in the harvest.

00:23:43.177 --> 00:24:12.673
You will see the animal bow down for a little bit, giving a window of time to move.

00:24:14.102 --> 00:24:44.786
The bear sat down and paused, but it was still ready to roar.

00:25:02.057 --> 00:25:11.720
It gave a window for revival in Russia and for things to happen with China.

00:25:15.155 --> 00:25:23.891
I saw the rising sun over Taiwan and the remnant church interceding.

00:25:26.124 --> 00:25:42.400
I saw it glowing with glory and a revival taking place.

00:25:48.560 --> 00:26:14.200
He needs you to help pray; that's why I called you to this channel to pray for Donald Trump.

00:26:14.200 --> 00:26:37.955
Brandon, I saw Donald Trump looking exhausted because of the pressure of the world on his shoulders.

00:26:37.955 --> 00:26:53.183
The Lord is using him for this season to bring forth revival.

00:26:53.183 --> 00:27:02.500
This is a small window—four years.

00:27:02.500 --> 00:27:23.700
If another plague tries to take place, the window would be even smaller.

00:27:23.700 --> 00:27:31.707
He cannot do this alone.

00:27:31.707 --> 00:27:55.697
As he steps into office, there will be a mantle on him on the 20th.

00:27:55.697 --> 00:28:10.679
I saw him cracking that whip, making those devils pop back.

00:28:10.679 --> 00:28:28.373
I saw Kim Jong-un, and the Lord called him the 'Pillsbury Doughboy.

00:28:28.373 --> 00:28:55.937
' The Lord was very angry and said He was going to humble him in a day.

00:28:55.937 --> 00:29:29.510
He has been in the way too long, and I will humble him like Pharaoh.

00:29:36.950 --> 00:29:40.372
His days on this earth are numbered.

00:29:40.372 --> 00:30:18.000
Even as he is eliminated, it will take out his sister, for she is just as much of a tyrant.

00:30:18.000 --> 00:30:43.469
There will be a crumbling of the infrastructure and great chaos in North Korea.

00:30:53.627 --> 00:31:17.088
The Iron Curtain that has held back the gospel will be broken, and My gospel will spread throughout North Korea.

00:31:17.088 --> 00:31:27.702
We've just started the Japan channel today.

00:31:27.702 --> 00:31:55.080
We're going to create channels for all the Asian people in all languages: Philippines, China, Vietnam, and South Korea.

00:31:55.080 --> 00:32:11.772
There will be a great harvest of souls in North Korea.

00:32:21.750 --> 00:32:44.039
I saw missionaries from South Korea going over the border and snatching people out of the pits of hell.

00:32:44.039 --> 00:33:01.020
The dynasties that have held these people back are going to crumble.

00:33:04.751 --> 00:33:34.013
I saw the military of North Korea trying to bring stability, reaching out to China to help find another leader.

00:33:34.013 --> 00:33:57.829
But the Lord is giving a window of great salvation with manifestations of glory.

00:33:57.829 --> 00:34:19.529
It will be a time of freedom and liberty that flows through North Korea and China.

00:34:19.529 --> 00:34:50.250
As we see Donald Trump come on the scene, I saw a cracking of the whip this year.

00:34:50.250 --> 00:35:00.760
I saw a champagne bottle that was shaken, building pressure.

00:35:00.760 --> 00:35:18.440
When he comes on the scene, I saw that cork go 'boom!

00:35:18.440 --> 00:35:38.575
' It was a time of celebration because of the anticipation for change.

00:35:39.373 --> 00:36:09.815
I saw an acceleration of the agenda with crypto taking off like a rocket ship through the first quarter.

00:36:09.815 --> 00:36:22.880
I believe there could be two different crashes.

00:36:22.880 --> 00:37:01.359
One was a plan to bring down the dollar ahead of time to bring in the One World Order fast, but the Lord is giving his bride a window.

00:37:01.359 --> 00:37:21.000
I saw the darkness lifting above the trees for a season.

00:37:21.000 --> 00:37:53.013
I warned you all over a year ago that Donald Trump would devise a plan for Canada and America to join.

00:37:57.955 --> 00:38:25.019
He is talking about tariffs now, but I saw Canada, America, and Mexico becoming one central currency with no financial borders.

00:38:25.019 --> 00:38:44.046
It was called Amero, is what I believe I heard the Lord say.

00:38:44.046 --> 00:38:50.507
It would make America stronger.

00:38:50.507 --> 00:39:09.296
Our dollar was depleted, and I saw a 1929-style economic crash.

00:39:19.732 --> 00:39:41.903
I saw the plane of America crash, and he built it back—not 'built back better,' but able to function.

00:39:41.903 --> 00:40:00.200
Donald Trump got behind the cockpit, and that plane was flying again.

00:40:09.820 --> 00:40:10.074
It was about bringing in the harvest.

00:40:21.095 --> 00:40:21.411
A great humbling is coming to America.

00:40:21.411 --> 00:40:33.086
I saw the Founding Fathers making a covenant.

00:40:34.113 --> 00:40:48.000
