00:40:48.000 --> 00:41:08.820
We have entered into compromise, and there were barely even a few threads left before that covenant was broken.

00:41:08.820 --> 00:41:28.697
But as Donald Trump made an alliance with Israel, it saved the contract.

00:41:29.743 --> 00:41:44.147
He bridged the gap and made that covenant a three-stranded cord.

00:41:58.000 --> 00:42:07.760
A golden glowing thread appeared as we blessed Israel, giving us a lifeline over America.

00:42:08.792 --> 00:42:28.816
I saw great natural gas and oil reserves in the Mediterranean and a flourishing of agriculture.

00:42:28.816 --> 00:42:55.335
The Father breathed on the Abrahamic covenant, and it was a freshening and a renewing of that covenant.

00:42:55.599 --> 00:43:16.212
I saw a major revival breaking out in Israel, with rabbis seeing Jesus as the Messiah.

00:43:16.212 --> 00:43:26.595
There will be Jewish people celebrating in the streets.

00:43:30.820 --> 00:43:44.980
I saw great prosperity, and that prosperity tried to come to America.

00:43:58.462 --> 00:43:58.751
I saw the remnant being blessed.

00:43:58.751 --> 00:44:09.340
There was light in Goshen and darkness in Egypt.

00:44:09.340 --> 00:44:37.470
There is a dividing line being set up right now, just like the children of Israel on Mount Sinai.

00:44:46.889 --> 00:44:52.692
