00:44:52.692 --> 00:45:26.348
There will be a great shaking in the body of Christ from 2025 through 2028 to awaken His church.

00:45:26.348 --> 00:46:01.862
He showed us with catchers' mitts on our hands, in position to catch the harvest because it's coming in fast.

00:46:01.862 --> 00:46:21.370
I saw terrorist attacks trying to take place in Europe, Toronto, Pennsylvania, and New York.

00:46:24.388 --> 00:46:31.240
You will see major earthquakes, storms, and volcanoes.

00:46:31.240 --> 00:46:41.360
Jesus is standing at the door.

00:46:49.105 --> 00:46:51.079
I encourage you to have great anticipation for 2025.

00:46:51.079 --> 00:47:17.680
Write your list of everything you're believing God for—nothing's too big or too small.

00:47:17.680 --> 00:47:31.240
Find scriptures to back up your faith.

00:47:31.240 --> 00:47:41.369
My son is busy creating these Asian channels to bring the harvest in.

00:47:46.546 --> 00:47:58.359
The Lord told me His people are believing too small.

00:47:58.359 --> 00:48:22.720
If you can think it and believe it, He will bring it to you.

00:48:22.720 --> 00:48:37.069
Like a child, believe that nothing is impossible for your Father.

00:48:42.960 --> 00:48:43.210
In 2025, we will thrive.

00:48:49.708 --> 00:48:54.079
It will be a year of great acceleration.

00:48:54.079 --> 00:49:00.233
Push yourself further.

00:49:00.233 --> 00:49:22.549
We're going to take communion now to close out this year.

00:49:30.996 --> 00:49:35.345
Father, we thank You for Your body and Your blood.

00:49:41.325 --> 00:49:51.800
We believe that by Your stripes we are healed.

00:49:52.640 --> 00:50:05.680
