00:52:11.949 --> 00:52:27.565
We are thriving in '25.

00:52:27.565 --> 00:52:44.559
We don't need luck; we have the blessing and favor of God.

00:52:45.188 --> 00:53:01.075
We lift up Donald Trump and thank You for his protection.

00:53:10.420 --> 00:53:16.972
